{"tid":1472490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突然]豬閪伯格正式宣佈與香港人作對","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T01:06:06.000Z","uid":207287,"like":152,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3c44ef093deac615456f76ee47b32fa13bca56","tid":1472490,"uid":207287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DYv9kvT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDYv9kvT.jpg&h=603618c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1vtA4r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1vtA4r.jpg&h=de558764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當我見到連三毛都咁多 like 嘅時候<br />\n唸住入去留個言 內容都係copy返嚟嗰啲：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共国网民你好，欢迎来到自由世界的互联网。 在这里你可以认识共产党不想你认识的事。 请随便发问：<br />\n- 六四事件<br />\n- 法轮功<br />\n- 新强集中营<br />\n- 小熊维尼<br />\n- 中共官员家人的外国国籍<br />\n- 艾未未<br />\n- 刘晓波<br />\n- 王全璋<br />\n- 反送中<br />\n- 民主与专制<br />\n- 一人一票<br />\n- 投票权<br />\n感谢你爱共产党并对独裁政权不想你认识的事件求真的态度<br />\n也感谢你爱自由世界的中华民族<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yndGbDW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyndGbDW.jpg&h=383a09b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">豬閪伯格我屌你老母！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\np.s. 第一次出po 有錯歡迎任屌"},{"pid":"5a8d944501d9a2a7891eb0296a9d2e0ec411316a","tid":1472490,"uid":207287,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我以為自己去咗微博"},{"pid":"9d8ec32db7c5281f09812deafd1ed300f97e6e79","tid":1472490,"uid":207287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid"