gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正常人個個都用Apple iMessage  <br />\n你地講就講到經常性緊急想人傳開去/ 保留事實真相，<br />\n但係你班傻鳩up load Facebook度人哋睇得link 嚟都俾人和諧消失晒，某程度上你依類人都係幫兇，<br />\n鬼唔望你地喺大陸突然被消失拎去打靶都無人知！咁鍾意用Facebook吖嗱？你班傻閪<br />\n<br />\n就算連登開咗Twitter 你見到都係得兩三萬人follow就知另外果九成人真係冇得救<br />\n明明大把選擇twitter 一樣可以Live + direct message <br />\nVimeo / Ello / twitter / 而家連Pinterest 都可以upload video<br />\n私人訊息可以Apple iMessage <br />\n電話加密通話可以FaceTime audio <br />\n搜尋器DuckDuckGo <br />\n平時非接觸式付款Apple pay <br />\n網絡瀏覽器用safari , 加埋嚟緊Apple sign in 強制取代Facebook / google sign in <br />\niMac pro / Mac Pro / Mac mini / MacBook 內置T2 保安晶片，鎖死加密成個OS，萬一真係想硬爆你部機攞料，係連啟動嘅第一步都做唔到，我肯定呢度九成九垃圾傻閪都係用windows !<br />\n你要講私隱講安全根本就睇你係咪真係有心去做"},{"pid":"64701a86744ea37293c0b7cc718e2ff5f9e51393","tid":1472490,"uid":207287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12629f2233c9ae50834ba7bf86353fa1361a97b0","tid":1472490,"uid":277589,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"太長炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"冇用 list 嘅話其實字數唔多 <br />\n可再測試"},{"pid":"a128594be072596cf265c9318e1e7b43252f5b16","tid":1472490,"uid":207287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc8eee2f418591b6b54e7da47031c1b5fdd20704","tid":1472490,"uid":207287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c7e6974faf7be7dfa3268657779ac72812f1d5e5","tid":1472490,"uid":248861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:13:51.000Z","msg":"仆街fb"},{"pid":"a370a9839181efcb9cb469b8bc8e8a9611d8b634","tid":1472490,"uid":111493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:14:47.000Z","msg":"香港Facebook好似好多大陸人打工？"},{"pid":"09fba00c705575acf2c06c7ba2ed518245c77d9c","tid":1472490,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:15:05.000Z"